It represents those that see the vision before everyone else. Together, the holders of these OG Passes will build the most unique NFT project that the world has ever seen. The OG Pass holders will have elite benefits including exclusive discord server access, a free NFT from the CKC NFT collection, voting power, entry in every single CKC giveaway, and many special surprises as the community grows.
